    "#### 4) Receive an integer as an input and, using a loop, calculate the factorial of this number, that is, the product of all the integers from one to the number provided. "
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "x = int(input())\n",
    "y = 1\n",
    "while y <= x :\n",
    "    print(x*y)\n",
    "    y += 1"
   ]
